<div class="container">
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
    <h4 class="emergency-description"><strong>To find a selection of appropriate responses to your emergency, choose the situation description below that is closest to yours.</strong></h4>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 emergency-type text-center">
        <%= link_to emergency_A_path do %>
          <h4>A: Emergency</h4>
          <p>If you or someone you know is seriously physically injured, unwell, or in serious physical danger (e.g. close to acting on suicidal thoughts)</p>
        <% end %>

      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 emergency-type text-center">
        <%= link_to emergency_B_path do %>
          <h4 >B: Urgent, but not life-threatening</h4>
          <p>If you or someone you know requires urgent care, but the situation is not life-threatening (e.g. self-harming but without life-threatening injuries, experiencing worsening symptoms of a pre-existing mental illness)</p>
        <% end %>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>
